TEXT.S: = Naihunpu = Gaga mniq Nantowseyn Sinyisyang ka alang Naihunpu. 656 sapah ka kneegu na sapah, 1,803 hiyi ka kana knhbragan na hiyi. Tnpusu seejiq o mangal 32% niqan 575 hiyi sp, rahuq na uxay tnpusu seejiq o mangal 68% niqan 1,228 hiyi koia. Kana ka kleegan seejiq ga, Bunun30%, Paiwan 1%, Tayal 0.5%, Amis 0.5%.
